fields.description:
Steps to Reproduce:
1. Launch Kitchen Sink
2. Click Base UI and click each item of the list and go back without actually running the test
3. View console from xCode

Actual Result:
[WARN] object: (null) was not of the right class: (null) is displayed after each launch

Expected Result:
Not to display the error messages

Note: 
Was not displaying warn messages on 1.6.2
fields.summary: iOS: [WARN] object: (null) was not of the right class: (null) each time you launch a test application
fields.environment: iPhone 4.3.2 with INFO Titanium SDK version: 1.7.0 (04/26/11 11:54 6b80fd9...)
